howtoplay.cauldron.text.5.notTouch=To dye Leather Armor or Leather Horse Armor, press :_input_key.use: on a Cauldron filled with water while holding the desired dye. This will change the color of the water inside of the Cauldron. Then dip your armor into the Cauldron by pressing :_input_key.use: with armor in your hand.                                    §r§7§o
howtoplay.cauldron.text.5.touch=To dye Leather Armor or Leather Horse Armor, tap a Cauldron filled with water while holding the desired dye. This will change the color of the water inside of the Cauldron. Then dip your armor into the Cauldron by tapping the Cauldron with the armor in your hand.              §r§7§o
howtoplay.cauldron.text.6=If you want to wash the dye off, dip the dyed item into a Cauldron of undyed Water.                                            §r§7§o
