howtoplay.npc.text.2=Only World Builders can place, delete, name, or edit NPCs. NPCs can execute commands and link to websites. Commands can be assigned to buttons in the NPC's dialog window; website links will always have a button.                                  §r§7§o
howtoplay.npc.text.3=NPCs have a variety of skins to choose from and are immobile.                     §r§7§o
