howtoplay.camera.text.1=The Camera allows players to take pictures in the world.                            §r§7§o
howtoplay.camera.text.2=To take a picture from your point of view, press :_input_key.use:.                  §r§7§o
howtoplay.camera.text.2.touch=To take a picture from your point of view, tap and hold, then release.            §r§7§o
howtoplay.camera.text.3=To take a selfie, place a camera and press :_input_key.use: on it.                  §r§7§o
howtoplay.camera.text.3.touch=To take a selfie, place a camera and tap the Take Picture button.                 §r§7§o
howtoplay.camera.text.4=Pictures can be viewed in the Portfolio or inserted into the Book and Quill.      §r§7§o
