howtoplay.classroomMode.text.1=Classroom Mode is an external application that provides educators with features designed to facilitate interaction with students. You can download Classroom Mode from the Minecraft Education website.                                             §r§7§o
howtoplay.classroomMode.text.2=As the host of a world, use the command /classroommode to launch the Classroom Mode app and connect it to Minecraft Education.                                   §r§7§o
