howtoplay.fishing.text.1=Fishing must be done with a Fishing Rod and is an excellent way to catch some fish or other cool items from the sea!   §r§7§o
howtoplay.fishing.header.1=Casting                                         §r§7§o
howtoplay.fishing.text.2.notTouch=Aim at a block of water and press :_input_key.use: while holding a fishing rod to cast the lure into the water.             §r§7§o
