howtoplay.fishing.text.3=Wait until you start to see a trail of bubbles coming for the lure.                  §r§7§o
howtoplay.fishing.text.4.notTouch=When the bubbles touch the lure, it will bob up and down. Press :_input_key.use: to reel in the lure. Be careful not to let your fish get away!                       §r§7§o
