howtoplay.food=Food                                            §r§7§o
howtoplay.food.title=How to Play: Food                            §r§7§o
howtoplay.food.text.1=You'll slowly get hungry during your adventures - fortunately the Overworld is full of food! You can gather apples from trees, meat from animals, or why not grow your own crops using a hoe?    §r§7§o
howtoplay.food.text.2.keyboard=To eat a food, select it in your hotbar, then click and hold the right mouse button. Keep the §ehunger bar§f:shank: full to regain health when you take damage.    §r§7§o§§
howtoplay.food.text.2.gamepad=To eat a food, select it in your hotbar, then press and hold :_input_key.use:. Keep the §ehunger bar§f:shank: full to regain health when you take damage.            §r§7§o§§
howtoplay.food.text.2.touch=To eat a food, select it in your hotbar, then tap the screen and hold. Keep the §ehunger bar§f:shank: full to regain health when you take damage.                    §r§7§o§§
howtoplay.food.text.3=Some raw foods are better when cooked first on a campfire or in a furnace - your tummy will thank you!                 §r§7§o
howtoplay.furnace=Furnace                                       §r§7§o
howtoplay.furnace.text.1=A Furnace allows you to cook or smelt items. For example, you can smelt Iron Ore into Iron Ingots.                         §r§7§o
howtoplay.furnace.text.2.notTouch=Place the Furnace in the world and press :_input_key.use: to use it.              §r§7§o
howtoplay.furnace.text.2.touch=Place the Furnace in the world and tap to use it.                                      §r§7§o
howtoplay.furnace.header.1=Fuel                                            §r§7§o
howtoplay.furnace.text.3=You need to put some fuel into the bottom of the Furnace, and the item that you want smelted in the top. The Furnace will then fire up and start working. Lots of things can be used as fuel; try experimenting with anything burnable!         §r§7§o
howtoplay.gameSettings=Game Settings                                 §r§7§o
howtoplay.gameSettings.text.1=When creating a world, you have many options. Below are the various settings that can be used to fine tune your experience. Don't worry if you didn't set them when you created the world, they can be changed at any time.                   §r§7§o
howtoplay.gameSettings.text.2=§eWorld Name§f: This is where you can name your world.                                   §r§7§o§§
howtoplay.gameSettings.text.3=§eDefault Game Mode§f: This is the gamemode that all new players to the world will start with. You can have players start in either survival or creative mode. Selecting creative mode will turn cheats on.                                                   §r§7§o§§
howtoplay.gameSettings.text.4=§eDifficulty§f: This setting affects how difficult the world will be. You can choose Peaceful, Easy, Normal, or Hard.            §r§7§o§§
