howtoplay.hostAndPlayerOptions.text.1.notTouch=When playing with cheats on, host options will allow you to teleport yourself or friends, change the weather, set the time of day, and change the entry point or world spawn of your game. Once cheats have been enabled, you can find these options in the chat window by pressing the [/] button next to the chat bar.                                                    §r§7§o
