howtoplay.minecoins.text.1=Explore a world of possibility with Minecoins: Minecraft's in-game currency! Minecoins let you add variety to your gameplay across supported Minecraft games.                                                 §r§7§o
howtoplay.minecoins.text.2=Once redeemed, your Minecoins are linked to your Microsoft account, so you can access your coins and purchases on other supported devices, too!          §r§7§o
