howtoplay.mounts.text.15.notTouch=Press :_input_key.sneak: to dismount.    §r§7§o
howtoplay.mounts.text.15a.touch=When using the D-Pad control scheme, tap :touch_jump: to dismount an animal.   §r§7§o
howtoplay.mounts.text.15b.touch=When using a Joystick control scheme, tap :tip_virtual_button_dismount: to dismount an animal.                                 §r§7§o
