howtoplay.gatheringResources.text.1=The world is full of resources, including §ebuilding blocks§f, §ecrafting materials§f, and §efood§f.                                          §r§7§o§§§§§§
howtoplay.gatheringResources.text.2.nottouch=You can §ebreak blocks§f with your bare hands to gather resources like dirt and wood. Aim at a block, then §epress and hold§f :_input_key.attack:  until it breaks and the resources drop.                       §r§7§o§§§§
