howtoplay.nightfall=Nightfall                                       §r§7§o
howtoplay.nightfall.text.1=In Minecraft, the sun rises and sets as you adventure in your world. As the sun sets, you must take precautions. There are many dangers at night!            §r§7§o
howtoplay.nightfall.header.1=Take Shelter                                  §r§7§o
howtoplay.nightfall.text.2=If you have not already, you will need a place to take shelter from the dark and what lurks within it. This can be as simple as a hole in the side of a hill or a small cabin in the forest.                   §r§7§o
howtoplay.nightfall.text.3=Be sure to block off all entrances, you may want to use a door so you can go in and out. If you have made a bed this is a good place to put it along with your Crafting Table and Furnace.            §r§7§o
howtoplay.nightfall.text.4=Also be sure to light up the area with torches, it may save your life.             §r§7§o
howtoplay.nightfallNew=Nightfall                                       §r§7§o
howtoplay.nightfallNew.title=How to Play: Nightfall                        §r§7§o
howtoplay.nightfall.new.text.1=When the sun starts to set, it's time to get ready.                                      §r§7§o
howtoplay.nightfall.new.text.2=At night, the Overworld is home to zombies, spiders, skeletons, and other dangerous creatures we call §ehostile mobs§f.    §r§7§o§§
howtoplay.nightfall.new.text.3=Crafting some §etorches§f can help you see in the dark, while also keeping mobs from spawning too close.                     §r§7§o§§
howtoplay.nightfall.new.text.4.keyboard=While holding a torch, place it into the world by right-clicking a nearby free surface.                                          §r§7§o
howtoplay.nightfall.new.text.4.gamepad=While holding a torch, place it into the world by pressing :_input_key.use:.        §r§7§o
howtoplay.nightfall.new.text.4.touch=While holding a torch, place it into the world by tapping a nearby free surface.                                                  §r§7§o
howtoplay.nightfall.new.text.4.touch.crosshair=While holding a torch, place it into the world by aiming at a nearby block and tapping :tip_virtual_button_action_build_or_use:.                                          §r§7§o
