howtoplay.weapons.header.3=Crossbow                                      §r§7§o
howtoplay.weapons.text.5.notTouch=The Crossbow is an alternate ranged weapon. Press and hold :_input_key.use: to load the crossbow. Once the Crossbow is loaded, it will stay loaded until it is fired. Press :_input_key.use: to fire an arrow. The Crossbow requires arrows to load.                                         §r§7§o
howtoplay.weapons.text.5a.touch=The crossbow is a ranged weapon which requires an arrow to be loaded. Tap and hold anywhere on the screen to load the crossbow with an arrow.            §r§7§o
